          <li><strong>Case:</strong> 41.5mm stainless steel, brushed and polished</li>
          <li><strong>Dial:</strong> Matte orange with applied Arabic numerals and baton indices</li>
          <li><strong>Bezel:</strong> 120-click unidirectional, black aluminum insert</li>
          <li><strong>Crystal:</strong> Flat mineral</li>
          <li><strong>Water Resistance:</strong> 200m (screw-down crown + pusher)</li>
          <li><strong>Complications:</strong> Day (English/Spanish) and date</li>
          <li><strong>Strap:</strong> Black polyurethane diver strap, 22mm lug width</li>
          <li><strong>Lume:</strong> Hands and indices, plus bezel pip</li>
          <li><strong>Power Reserve:</strong> ~40 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Price:</strong> $121.89</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="story-cta">
        <p>Every collection starts somewhere. Let the Mako be your beginning — or your next great find.</p>
